@startuml
title Use Case Diagram - Personal Website

actor User as U

rectangle "Personal Website" {
    usecase "Melihat profil pemilik website" as UC1
    usecase "Melihat informasi umum tentang Roblox" as UC2
    usecase "Melihat informasi umum tentang Mobile Legend" as UC3
    usecase "Melihat informasi umum tentang GitHub" as UC4
    usecase "Melihat detail informasi Roblox" as UC5
    usecase "Melihat detail informasi Mobile Legend" as UC6
    usecase "Melihat detail informasi GitHub" as UC7
}

U --> UC1
U --> UC2
U --> UC3
U --> UC4
UC2 --> UC5 : <<extend>>
UC3 --> UC6 : <<extend>>
UC4 --> UC7 : <<extend>>

note right of U
  Tujuan User:
  - Mengetahui info umum & detail
  - Tentang Roblox, ML, dan GitHub
end note

@enduml
